{"type":"message","id":"13ceb586","parentId":"d2133add","timestamp":"2026-03-07T02:17:41.505Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"stock-watcher 脚本显示的列表与 stock-watchlist.json 文件不同，说明存在多个股票来源。接下来需要调用股票监控技能来获取更详细的实时行情数据。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"我注意到你的 watchlist 比 json 文件里的多！看起来还有一些其他来源的股票。让我用 stock-monitor-skill 来获取这些股票的详细行情数据。\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_44d62c540b1d4f0080db3e1f","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace && python -c \"\nimport urllib.request\nimport json\n\nstocks = [\n    ('601857', '中国石油'),\n    ('601808', '中海油服'),\n    ('600256', '广汇能源'),\n    ('600583', '海油工程'),\n    ('000852', '石化机械'),\n    ('600547', '山东黄金'),\n    ('601069', '西部黄金'),\n    ('600988', '赤峰黄金'),\n    ('000975', '银泰黄金'),\n    ('002716', '金贵银业'),\n    ('601899', '紫金矿业')\n]\n\nprint('📊 今日股票行情摘要 | 2026-03-07')\nprint('=' * 50)\nprint()\n\nfor code, name in stocks:\n    try:\n        url = f'http://hqdata.niuer2.net/{code}.json'\n        req = urllib.request.Request(url, headers={'User-Agent': 'Mozilla/5.0'})\n        resp = urllib.request.urlopen(req, timeout=5)\n        data = json.loads(resp.read().decode('utf-8'))\n        \n        if 'data' in data and 'price' in data['data']:\n            price = data['data']['price']\n            change = data['data']['change']\n            pct = data['data']['pct']\n            volume = data['data'].get('volume', '')\n            amount = data['data'].get('amount', '')\n            \n            # Format colors (red up, green down)\n            change_symbol = '🔺' if float(change) >= 0 else '🔻'\n            color = '🔴' if float(change) >= 0 else '🟢'\n            \n            print(f'{color} {name} ({code})')\n            print(f'   现价：¥{price}')\n            print(f'   涨跌：{change_symbol} {change:.2f} ({pct:.2f}%)')\n            print()\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f'⚠️ {name}: 获取失败')\n        print()\n\"\n"}}],"